        jLabel7.setText("<html>\n\nIt is particularly useful for:<br>\n <ul>\n<li>presenting and interpreting experimental data.<br>\n<li>attacking problems not amenable to a direct theoretical solution.<br>\n<li>checking equations.<br>\n<li>stablishing the relative importance of particular physical phenomena.<br>\n<li>physical modelling.\n</ul>\n</html>");
